description.fr: L'intrusion de {CharacterName:708} et {CharacterName:474} dans le repaire de la Déesse a excité les Shushus, ils remontent maintenant à la surface. {CharacterName:474} compte sur vous pour protéger {WorldZone:208[Astrub]}.
description.en: The {CharacterName:708} and {CharacterName:474}'s intrusion into the goddess's lair has riled up the Shushus, and they're now coming up to the surface. {CharacterName:474} is counting on you to protect {WorldZone:208[Astrub]}.
description.es: La intrusión de {CharacterName:708} y {CharacterName:474} en la guarida de la diosa ha espabilado a los fab'huritus, y ahora están saliendo a la superficie. {CharacterName:474} cuenta contigo para proteger {WorldZone:208[Astrub]}.
description.de: Dass {CharacterName:708} und {CharacterName:474} in die Höhle der Göttin eingedrungen sind, hat die Shushus in große Aufregung versetzt. Sie kehren nun an die Oberfläche zurück. {CharacterName:474} verlässt sich darauf, dass du {WorldZone:208[Astrub]} beschützt.
description.pt: A intrusão de {CharacterName:708} e {CharacterName:474} no esconderijo da deusa atiçou os Shushus e, agora, eles subiram à superfície. {CharacterName:474} conta com você para proteger {WorldZone:208[Astrub]}.

descriptionFinished.fr: {CharacterName:474}, {CharacterName:596} et {CharacterName:708} ont repoussé l'assaut des Shushus Majeurs, mais de nouvelles batailles sont à craindre. Ils doivent élaborer un plan d'action.
descriptionFinished.en: {CharacterName:474}, {CharacterName:596} and {CharacterName:708} pushed back the Major Shushus' offensive, but new battles are to be feared. They need to come up with a plan of action.
descriptionFinished.es: {CharacterName:474}, {CharacterName:596} y {CharacterName:708} han frenado el asalto de los fab'huritus mayores, pero temen que pueda haber nuevas batallas. Deben elaborar un plan de acción.
descriptionFinished.de: {CharacterName:474}, {CharacterName:596} und {CharacterName:708} haben den Sturmangriff der großen Shushus abgewehrt, es sind jedoch weitere Schlachten zu befürchten. Sie müssen einen Maßnahmenplan ausarbeiten.
descriptionFinished.pt: {CharacterName:474}, {CharacterName:596} e {CharacterName:708} impediram o avanço dos Shushus Maiores, mas novos combates estão por vir. Eles precisam elaborar um plano de ação.
